cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the application of Deep Learning in image recognition, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions the transformation of time-series data into image data format, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The use of Deep Belief Network and Adaptive Structural Learning method relates to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
